metadata.name: Luna #1/1
metadata.description:
Luna was a beautiful, full-bodied goddess, equipped with a accoutrements that emitted pulsing purple energy and dazzling lasers. Her appearance might have been intimidating, but her energy  one of love and positive energy. often scantily clad or dressed in leather harnesses that accentuated her curves.

Luna was a guardian of the universe, and she had been tasked with keeping it safe from all forms of darkness and evil. She possessed incredible strength and power, The stars and planets spun on their axes around her, pulsing with energy as she passed by. 

Luna's weapon glowed with an intense purple light. She channeled all her love and positive energy into it, using it to overcome darkness gazing out into the infinite expanse of space.
